  "texts": [
    "This study examines the shared outcomes and objectives of STEM professional development projects for STEM integration in China and the impact of these projects on STEM teachers' competencies and teaching practices, which are directly linked to how the factors and variables influence the outcomes of these projects.",
    "Various pedagogical initiatives were also examined, each intended to enhance teachers' ability to deliver STEM content effectively.",
    "These varied programs, rich in collaborative and reflective practices, have shown us the vibrant potential of educational innovation.",
    "Nevertheless, gaps were identified during this exploration.",
    "Although highly regarded studies with substantial individual merit often operate in isolation without a coherent framework."
